{"name": "movoid-config", "metadata": {"name": "movoid-config", "version": "1.2.6", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": null, "upload_time": 1729786637}, "documentation": ["This is a simple program for developer to create a param-config reader.\nIt only needs config_dict and config_file_name to analyse all param and config\n\nfor example,your py file main.py is\n\n```python\nfrom movoid_config import Config\n\nconfig = Config({\n    \"param\": {\n        \"type\": \"string\",  # we will change it to a string.you can input: int,float,number,bool,true,false,list,dict,enum,kv,byte.others are all string.\n        \"default\": \"ppp\",  # when you do not input,we will give a default value.it will make 'must' invalidate\n        \"single\": \"p\",  # use like -p *\n        \"full\": \"param\",  # use like --param *\n        \"key\": \"param\",  # use like param=?\n        \"ini\": [\"main\", \"param\"],  # use in config.ini\n        \"config\": True,  # whether try to find and write in .ini file\n        \"must\": True,  # whether you must input it ,or it will raise exception\n        \"ask\": True,  # when you do not input,you can change to ask user to input it\n        \"help\": \"This is param which is an example.\",  # show it in help text.(not done yet)\n    },\n    \"check\": {\n        \"type\": \"true\",\n        \"false\": {\n            \"single\": \"f\",\n            \"full\": \"false\"\n        }  # when type is true,you can input -f or --false to input a false value to \"check\"\n    },\n    \"int_list\": {\n        \"full\": \"list\",\n        \"type\": \"list\",\n        \"sub\": \"int\"  # to define type of list value\n    },\n    \"int_bool_dict\": {\n        \"key\": \"dict\",\n        \"type\": \"dict\",\n        \"sub\": [\"int\", \"str\"]  # to define type of dict key and value\n    }\n}, \"config.ini\")\n\nprint(config.param)\nprint(config[\"int_list\"])\nprint(config[\"int_bool_dict\"])\n\n```\n\nwhen you input \n```shell\npython main.py -p p234 --list 1,2,3 dict=1:a,2:b\n```\nyou can see \n```shell\np234\n[1, 2, 3]\n{1: 'a', 2: 'b'}\n```\n\nyou can also use \n```python\nfrom movoid_config import Config\n\nconfig = Config({})\nfor i, v in config.items():\n    print(i, v)\nfor i in config.keys():\n    print(i)\nfor v in config.values():\n    print(v)\n```\nto traversal loop\n\nIf you use when you do not input. An error will be raised like use an unknown key in a dict.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "movoid_config", "documentation": ["# File          : __init__.py\n# Author        : Sun YiFan-Movoid\n# Time          : 2024/1/1 11:52\n# Description   : ", "! /usr/bin/env python3", "-*- coding: utf-8 -*-"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "movoid_config.CmdLoopRun", "xref": {"fqname": "movoid_config.loop_run.CmdLoopRun", "project": null}}, {"name": "movoid_config.Config", "xref": {"fqname": "movoid_config.config.Config", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "movoid_config.loop_run", "documentation": ["# File          : loop_run\n# Author        : Sun YiFan-Movoid\n# Time          : 2024/2/6 20:17\n# Description   : ", "! /usr/bin/env python3", "-*- coding: utf-8 -*-"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "movoid_config.loop_run.CmdLoopRun", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "movoid_config.loop_run.CmdLoopRun.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "start_now", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "**kwargs", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "movoid_config.loop_run.CmdLoopRun.init_config", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "movoid_config.loop_run.CmdLoopRun.start", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "movoid_config.loop_run.CmdLoopRun.start_main", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "movoid_config.loop_run.CmdLoopRun.start_exception", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "movoid_config.loop_run.CmdLoopRun.start_end", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "movoid_config.loop_run.CmdLoopRun.start_exit", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "movoid_config.config", "documentation": ["# File          : config\n# Author        : Sun YiFan-movoid\n# Time          : 2024/1/1 12:27\n# Description   : ", "! /usr/bin/env python3", "-*- coding: utf-8 -*-"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "movoid_config.config.Config", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "movoid_config.config.Config.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "_dict", "type": {"name": "Union", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Union", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Dict", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "_file", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "_file_write", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["\u53ef\u4ee5\u76f4\u63a5\u8bbe\u7f6e\u53c2\u6570\u7c7b\